{Name}{}{none}
{Speech 1}{}{Predialogue installations}
{Speech 1 Answer 2}{}{Answer text}
{Speech 2}{}{[Smirks] Well, what do you want, pajamas?}
{Speech 2 Answer Exit}{}{Ohhh [Leave]}
{Speech 2 Answer 3}{}{Out of the way, oaf!}
{Speech 2 Answer 4}{}{What's this, sir?}
{Speech 2 Answer 7}{}{Who are you, sir?}
{Speech 3}{}{Hm. You're taking on too much! I'll teach you a lesson.}
{Speech 3 Answer Exit}{}{Now we'll see who teaches whom a lesson![Attack]}
