{Speech 4}{}{This? [Shows you a clenched fist] Your ticket to a better life, rookie. Want to give it a try? [Guffaws]}
{Speech 4 Answer 5}{}{No, thanks. I mean, what is it you're guarding here?}
{Speech 5}{}{This is the barracks and training camp of the rangers, @sex@|son|sweetheart|. Want to join?}
{Speech 5 Answer 6}{}{Maybe. What do I have to do for that?}
{Speech 6}{}{Ah, hell if I know. Ask Sergeant Kyle inside, or find Eliza in the town center.}
{Speech 6 Answer Exit}{}{Thanks, I'll give it a shot. [Leave]}
{Speech 7}{}{I'm your favorite grandma, @sex@|son|sweetheart|! [Guffaws] Don't you recognize me?}
{Speech 7 Answer Exit}{}{Your jokes are stupid. Not funny. [Leave]}
